---
title: Cacciatore-Style Slow-Cooked Chicken with Veggies & Couscous
description: It’s always nice to slow down once in a while and these slow-cooked chicken drumsticks are perfect for doing just that. The chicken
is baked to absorb the mouth-watering taste of the tomato, herbs and mushroom sauce. Make a fluffy couscous to serve alongside
it and we promise this dish will be worth the wait.

